<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .success-box {
      background-color: #d4edda;
      border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>✅ Email Changed Successfully</h2>
    <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
    
    <div class="success-box">
      <strong>Your email address has been successfully updated!</strong><br><br>
      <strong>New email:</strong> {{email}}
    </div>
    
    <p>This email address is now associated with your <strong>{{appName}}</strong> account.</p>
    <p>You can now log in with your new email address.</p>
    
    <p>Click the button below to log in:</p>
    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">🔐 Log In Now</a>
    
    <p>If you did not make this change, please contact our support team immediately at <a href="{{supportUrl}}">{{supportUrl}}</a>.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>{{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>